javmos.components

Class JavmosComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • javmos.components.JavmosComponent
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CartesianPlane, Function, Point

    public abstract class JavmosComponent
extends java.lang.Object
    This abstract class serves as a template for all Javmos components. You cannot add any other methods nor modify the method signatures.
